<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prayer-n">prayer <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /preə(r)/    美 /prer/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>祈祷 (的内容)；祈祷文：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>say / give one’s prayers 
做祷告</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>祈祷 (的行为)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>kneel down in prayer 
跪下祈祷</p></div></div>